<li><a href="https://www.baselayer.com/company/careers/" rel="nofollow">Baselayer</a> - Data center and infrastructure management software.</li>
<li><a href="http://bashojobs.theresumator.com" rel="nofollow">Basho</a> - Creators of Riak, an open source platform and k/v database. We code in Erlang and hang out on clouds. Everyone works remote and gets together a few times a year at HQ in Seattle.</li>
<li><a href="http://bebanjo.com/careers/" rel="nofollow">BeBanjo</a> - Software as a service for managing video on-demand. Ruby / Rails, Elasticsearch, Sidekiq.</li>
